entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You spoke to Herron. He wants you to wait until he is done decrypting the data.
entries.journal_entry_description: Give the data disk to Herron and see if you can get any details.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to Mos Taike and see if you can locate Cale Herron somewhere within the town limits.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: What is your progress?  We heard the Mos Eisley Laboratory had been ransacked and a biologist was killed. Why did you not check in?  Jabba wants results! Do not fail us again.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find out if Cale knows anything new.
